description:
Why hasn’t Jesus returned yet? Jesus is working in the heavenly tabernacle right now, representing those who have chosen him as their Savior. As we, on earth, are charged with telling the world about God’s love, Jesus works on our behalf in Heaven so we can spend forever with Him. 

Blog: https://www.ibelievebible.com/the-heavenly-sanctuary/
